    dc:creator "Rodriguez, Pilar; Vučković, Natalija; Kerovec, Mladen" ;
    dc:date "2020" ;
    dc:title "New species of aquatic oligochaetes (Annelida: Clitellata) from tufa barriers in Croatia" ;
